In [4]:
df['Cel V']=df['Cell V']*(df['Pixel size']**3)
df['Cel S']=df['Cell S']*(df['Pixel size']**2)

df['Nuc V']=df['Nucleus V']*(df['Pixel size']**3)
df['Nuc S']=df['Nucleus S']*(df['Pixel size']**2)
In [5]:
plt.figure(figsize=(5,5), dpi=600)
sns.set(font='sans serif')
sns.set(style="whitegrid")

ax=sns.boxplot(x=df['Sample preparation'], y=df['Nuc V'], data=df)
    
comparisons = [("live_adherent", "fixed")]

annotator = Annotator(ax, comparisons, data=df, x="Sample preparation", y="Nucleus V")
annotator.configure(test='t-test_ind', text_format='star', loc='inside', verbose=2)
annotator.apply_and_annotate()

ax.set(xticklabels=["live", "fixed"])  
ax.tick_params(axis='x', labelsize=15)
ax.set(xlabel=None)
ax.tick_params(axis='y', labelsize=15)
ax.set_ylabel("Nucleus volume", fontsize=18)          
#plt.ylim(0.05,0.3)
